        public IDocDocumentList(com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocumentList jcoDocumentList)
        Creates a document list using the passed IDocDocumentList. New documents can be added corresponding to the IDoc repository used for this document list.
        Parameters:
        jcoDocumentList - A document list that should be wrapped to be used with the Adapter for SAP.
